Customer Management
Sections
1. Unverified Users
• Newly registered users
• Admin can:
o Approve user
2. Verified Users
• Approved users
• Actions:
o Inactivate/Delete
3. Deleted / Inactive Users
• Inactive users list


Session Management
Requirements
• Maintain session after login
• Destroy session on logout
• Protect routes using middleware

